      "num": 1,
      "geez": "ወእምህየ፡ ሖርኩ፡ መንገለ፡ ዐረብ፡ በአጽናፈ፡ ምድር፡ ወርኢኩ፡ በህየ፡ ሠለስተ፡ ኀዋኅወ፡ ሰማይ፡ ርኅዋተ፡ በከመ፡ ርኢኩ፡ በምሥራቁ፡ ወበአምጣነ፡ ኀዋኅዉ፡ ወበአምጣነ፡ ሙፃኡ።",
      "translation": "And from thence I went towards the west to the ends of the earth, and saw there three portals of the heaven open such as I had seen in the †east†, the same number of portals, and the same number of outlets.",
